data.description: Location Location Location!!! This extremely spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home is located just minutes away from Hwy 281, Hwy 1604, I35, I410, San Antonio International Airport. Even better, a HEB is close for your grocery shopping needs. Not to mention, you have private access to the McAllister Park trails.   As you enter the home, you will be pleased to see brand new wood floors and a large welcoming space.  This home boasts 3 living areas, which is an entertainers dream. In the kitchen you will enjoy freshly installed granite countertops and plenty of room to host an event with ample bar space. The main living room is so big that you can fit a large sectional and many more pieces of furniture. As you walk up stairs you will be welcomed to a game room that divides the bedrooms from each other. The master bedroom, at the end of the hall, easily fits a king sized bed and all of your dressers with even room to spare! The master bathroom has been fully remodeled and looks amazing!! The Master closet can fit even the largest of wardrobes.   Each oversized secondary bedroom has ample space and area for all of your children and guests. The back yard has a covered patio and a trellis, with plenty of room to enjoy the outdoors. Come make this your home today.
